# Mapty

From the course The Complete JavaScript Course 2022: From Zero to Expert! by Jonas Schmedtmann

Additional features added

* Hide the form when esc is pressed
* Properly load workout objects from local storage
* Pop up error messages rather than using alert
* Edit a workout
* Delete a workout
* Sort workouts
* Reset all data
* Zoom map to show all workouts

In action at https://mapty.thefifthcontinent.com/